{"about_the_game":"<strong>Stranded on a frigid mining outpost, you must protect the reactor that powers your distress beacon from hordes of gloops- squishy slimes that attack with plasma projectiles! Collect items, set up sentries, defeat bosses, and fight to survive in this highly replayable twin-stick wave-defense roguelike.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIGHT</h2>Defend the outpost from relentless swarms of enemies. Play from a cast of grizzled mercenaries, each with unique weapons, items, and abilities! Dodge attacks by combat rolling and make every bullet count!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/Fight_Gif_Store_Fast.gif?t=1725400851\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUY</h2>Spend scrap at shops to buy curious items and increase your fighting power. Pick up items that synergize well with each other to create a limitless number of unique builds. Take your chances with the store's random option to get legendary items for cheap. Complete challenging achievements to unlock new items, playable characters, and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/Shop_Cycle.gif?t=1725400851\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PREPARE</h2>Adapt to survive as enemies break through barricades and find new paths to attack from. Utilize teleporters, vents, doors, and a drawbridge to control the flow of combat and give yourself an edge in battle. You can also spend scrap on sentry turrets and automated drones to bolster your defenses!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/Prepare_Gif.gif?t=1725400851\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE</h2><br>Shoot, dodge, and blast your way to victory as you defend the outpost's reactor until reinforcements arrive.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778200/extras/Survive_